      "message": "did you mean u|x|y|z? Otherwise I don\u0027t understand why | and / are used interchangably... If it is indeed \u0027/\u0027 please leave a not explaining that LOGDOG_NAMESPACE uses \u0027/\u0027 instead of \u0027|\u0027 as a separator (also, is there escaping?)",
